name: Return Heli Airport Parking
description:
Return Heli Airport Parking is a joyful task. You have to park many Vehicles before. This time you have to park a Heli in a Airport. You have to park Heli in a given time. You have choice of heli selection. Select your Heli which you like. And park the Heli. In every level, their are different locations for parking. In this way you can enhance your parking abilities in a best way.
Features:
- Realistic helicopter and control
- Highly graphics
- High quality modern helicopters
- Multi missions and tasks
- Beautiful game and game play sounds
